summary: An ordinance repealing Ordinance No. 15614 entitled: "An ordinance relating to and providing for the improvement of, all in accordance with Resolution No. 8th Avenue Northeast in the City of Seattle from East 55th Street to East 65th Street, by grading and curbing the same, in accordance with Resolution No. 471, of the city council of the City of Seattle; and providing payment therefor by the mode of "Payment in Bonds", as provided by the laws of the State of Washington and the Charter and Ordinances of the City of Seattle.
